    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Planet Hoarders</strong> is a co-op game where you <strong>collect</strong> cute creatures to meet your <strong>quota</strong> in dark dungeons… and <strong>hide</strong> from the not-so-cute ones.<br>You’re a replicant, grown by the Corporation for this exact mission.<br>Will you obey without question?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291090/extras/1985d879cb9113ba8d9f825c7cd35fa2.poster.avif?t=1766871149\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291090/extras/1985d879cb9113ba8d9f825c7cd35fa2.webm?t=1766871149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291090/extras/1985d879cb9113ba8d9f825c7cd35fa2.mp4?t=1766871149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>COOPERATE TO SURVIVE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Split up or stick together? You’ll need teamwork to solve co-op-only <strong>puzzles</strong> and carry precious cargo back to the ship.<br>Or just <strong>slap</strong> someone to stop them from panicking.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291090/extras/7564970141cf72ca9c6f428bc2754d19.poster.avif?t=1766871149\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291090/extras/7564970141cf72ca9c6f428bc2754d19.webm?t=1766871149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291090/extras/7564970141cf72ca9c6f428bc2754d19.mp4?t=1766871149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>EXPLORE DEADLY PLANETS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each landing zone hides a <strong>procedurally-generated</strong> dungeon where danger and profit grow the deeper you go. <br>Higher risk, higher payout.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291090/extras/b793d97b7204d32ab320d6c6ec5bbc3f.poster.avif?t=1766871149\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291090/extras/b793d97b7204d32ab320d6c6ec5bbc3f.webm?t=1766871149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291090/extras/b793d97b7204d32ab320d6c6ec5bbc3f.mp4?t=1766871149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BECOME A PROP (LITERALLY)</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Too scared? Turn into a <strong>cube</strong>. Enemies might ignore you.<br>Teammates might <strong>step</strong> <strong>on</strong> you. Or <strong>drag</strong> you.<br>Blend in. Or die trying.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291090/extras/8c95b1908755f7970e5b045ff77cb7fd.poster.avif?t=1766871149\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291090/extras/8c95b1908755f7970e5b045ff77cb7fd.webm?t=1766871149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291090/extras/8c95b1908755f7970e5b045ff77cb7fd.mp4?t=1766871149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DON’T BECOME PREY</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Monsters</strong> roam the dungeons. Some hunt by sound.<br>Some stalk. Some rush. All are hungry.<br>Keep Corp. property (you) safe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291090/extras/075304be86adc060c928a826fd6ca0df.poster.avif?t=1766871149\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291090/extras/075304be86adc060c928a826fd6ca0df.webm?t=1766871149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291090/extras/075304be86adc060c928a826fd6ca0df.mp4?t=1766871149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>EQUIP YOURSELF</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy gear on the ship: jump-pads, medkits, creature lures, and more.<br>Define your playstyle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291090/extras/54fe08fe2aec37cd48ff328336b4231a.poster.avif?t=1766871149\" width=600 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291090/extras/54fe08fe2aec37cd48ff328336b4231a.webm?t=1766871149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3291090/extras/54fe08fe2aec37cd48ff328336b4231a.mp4?t=1766871149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hunt with up to 4 replicants (friends)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Communicate via proximity chat or walkie-talkies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 planets to land on (and probably die on)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8+ monsters to scream at</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A hammer to stun and capture creatures</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bunch of upgrades and gear</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Procedurally-generated dungeons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A caring, loving Corporation (legally obligated to say that)</p></li></ul>",
